Placed an order for (2) 4 chicken wings with pork fried rice. Not only did I wait 1 1/2+ hours for delivery (located 7 blocks away), I only received one order of 4 chicken wings with pork fried rice. On top of that they scam you by chopping up the chicken wings. I received 3 drums and 3 flats which is  only 3 chicken wings. I'll stick with atomic wings.

When I first started ordering from this establishment, I had no issues and enjoyed their service and food. As of lately, I have received frustrating service and experience. I have ordered several times before finally doing this review. Starting with the individual who answers the phone for orders. That person is rude. At first, I thought they were not having a good day or called at the wrong time. We are all humans. However, this person is always rude, and what confirmed it was my coworker experiencing the same thing. They send incomplete orders and will not admit it. The last time I ordered from this establishment, they were missing directive, and after calling, we became more frustrated. They are late with the delivery consistently, and they treat it with no care. Finally, they burn the food; the 1/2 chicken we received was burnt down to the bone. Their customer service is disrespectful, and when asked for a refund, they denied it. They are going in the wrong direction—such A HUGE SHAME
